        "Language Learning Should Be Free & Collaborative"
      </h2>
      <p class="font-primary text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        Forget expensive apps and private platforms. Bridge creates
        comprehensive language courses built by the community, combining
        structured lessons, vocabulary, and real-world content to make quality
        education accessible to everyone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

